# superclaude-instructions/07-mobile-conversion.yaml
name: Mobile Conversion
description: Preps for Android/iOS apps.
commands:
  - command: /migrate --react-native --persona-frontend --evidence --seq
    prompt: |
      Convert web app to React Native for Android/iOS: Adapt UI components, API calls, gallery/auth. Notes for Google Play/App Store submission, including Firebase setup.
      Remember to use your tools: --persona-frontend for UI adaptation, --seq for conversion steps, --evidence for app store guidelines.
    output: docs/mobile-guide.md
    notes: |
      - Run command with SuperClaude to generate docs/mobile-guide.md.
      - Install Expo: `npm install -g expo-cli`.
      - Share guide with Grok for review. Rerun with --uc if needed.